<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-38-0220 </DOCNO><TEXT>The concept of the development of Czechoslovak nuclear power reckons withthe construction of a nuclear power plant with two WWER-1000 units inthe Opatovice locality. The project places high demand on the accomodationand transport of personnel. The problems of the project are discussedand their solution suggested. With regard to the age structure of personnelthe necessity is pointed out of providing adequate places in creches,nursery schools and primary schools for their children. (J.B.). 4 refs.</TEXT></DOC>